{
  "chapter": 20,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十回\"寻寻觅觅\"，风四娘与沈璧君决定一同寻找萧十一郎。金凤凰在客厅醉酒，风四娘用激将法套出\"枫林渡口\"四字，金凤凰随后得意地承认自己故意说谎误导。众人赶往枫林渡口，途中在茶亭问路，卖酒老人告知需一天一夜才能到达。霍英无意间提到\"八仙船\"妓院，风四娘追问得知一个姓鱼的豪客包下了八仙船，遂改道春江城。抵达八仙船后，众人发现鲨王鱼吃人、金菩萨、厉青锋、人上人、轩辕三成、轩辕三缺等人全部死于一刀之下。唯一的幸存者张果老装死逃过一劫，她描述凶手是个好看的男人，手持一把好快好快的刀，指向萧十一郎。沈璧君认定萧十一郎是凶手，悲愤离去。风四娘留在院中，张果老随后死去，真凶身份成谜。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "现在你又是连夫人了，所以萧十一郎已经可以死了，他死了之后，你们就可以回到你们的无垢山庄做一双人人羡慕的无垢侠侣，就算萧十一郎的尸骨已喂了野狗，也跟你完全没有关系。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我却一定要去救他，所以我的话一说完，就非走不可。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我跟你一起走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "真的！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这次你真的下了决心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "不管怎么样，我要再见他一面。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你知不知道连城璧他们到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "难道你不知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "金凤凰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来，再添二十杯，我们一个人干十杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "是她自己要找我拼酒的，我想不答应都不行。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "金凤凰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你们的悄悄话说完了没有？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "金凤凰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你敢不敢过来跟我拼拼酒？",
      "tone": "挑衅",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "金凤凰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我就知道你不敢的，你武功虽然不错，可是你敢跟我拼酒，我非叫你喝得躺在地上不可。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "text": "你自己现在已经快躺下去了，我劝你还是少喝两杯的好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "金凤凰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你说我醉了？好，我们一个人干十杯，看看倒下去的是谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "金凤凰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "好，你不理我也没关系，只可惜你永远也找不到他们了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "text": "你能找得到他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "金凤凰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "周至刚是我的老公，我若找不到他，还有谁能找得到他？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "text": "你知道他在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "金凤凰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我当然知道，只可惜我偏偏不告诉你。除非你过来跟我赔个礼，再陪我喝十杯酒。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "text": "我看你是在吹牛。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "金凤凰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我吹什么牛？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "text": "你老公要到什么地方去，绝不会告诉你的，我知道。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "金凤凰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你知道个屁。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "text": "我的老婆若是个像你这么样的老太婆，我出去的时候也绝不会告诉她的，因为我要出去找花枝招展的大姑娘。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "金凤凰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "谁说他是去找女人了，他明明是要到枫林渡口去，他……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们走。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我们到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_huo_ying",
      "text": "当然是枫林渡口。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "金凤凰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "风四娘，风四娘，你总算也上了我一个当……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "金凤凰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不是老太婆……我不是……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "枫林渡口应该往哪条路走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yin",
      "speaker_name": "杜吟",
      "listener": "char_huo_ying",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_du_yin",
      "text": "我知道黄河上有个枫林渡口。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yin",
      "speaker_name": "杜吟",
      "listener": "char_huo_ying",
      "text": "江南没有黄河，只有长江。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_du_yin",
      "text": "长江的枫林渡口，我就没听说过了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yin",
      "speaker_name": "杜吟",
      "listener": "char_huo_ying",
      "text": "你没听说过，一定有人听说过的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我们不如就在前面停下来问问路，随便喝点酒，吃点东西。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yin",
      "speaker_name": "杜吟",
      "listener": "char_huo_ying",
      "text": "对，吃饱了才有力气办事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "这味道嗅起来好像还不错，一定也不会难吃。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_huo_ying",
      "text": "我不该带你来的，你太好吃。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这附近是不是也有个枫林渡口？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_jiu_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖酒老人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "有的，就在枫林镇外面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_mai_jiu_lao_ren",
      "text": "枫林镇要从哪条路走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_jiu_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖酒老人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "靠右手的这条。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_mai_jiu_lao_ren",
      "text": "远不远？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_jiu_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖酒老人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "不太远。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_mai_jiu_lao_ren",
      "text": "既然不太远，我们就可以吃饱了再赶路，反正天黑的时候能赶到就行了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_jiu_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖酒老人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "若是骑马去，明天天黑之前一定能赶到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_mai_jiu_lao_ren",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_jiu_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖酒老人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我……我什么也没有说。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_mai_jiu_lao_ren",
      "text": "你说我们要明天晚上才能到得了枫林镇。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_jiu_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖酒老人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "最快也得明天晚上，这段路快马也得走一天一夜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_mai_jiu_lao_ren",
      "text": "要走一天一夜的路，你还说不太远？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_jiu_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖酒老人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "一个人至少要活好几十年，只走一天路，又怎么能算多？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_mai_jiu_lao_ren",
      "text": "从这里去有没有近路？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_jiu_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖酒老人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "没有。就算有，我也不知道，我这一辈子，从来也没有走过近路，所以我才能活得比人长些。我今年已七十九。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_du_yin",
      "text": "看来这老头子跟八仙船的张果老倒是天生的一对儿。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_huo_ying",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我……我没有说什么。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_huo_ying",
      "text": "你刚才是不是在说八仙船？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "好像是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_huo_ying",
      "text": "这条船在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "那不是条船，是个……是个妓院。",
      "tone": "尴尬",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "那妓院里有八位姑娘，外号叫八仙，最滑稽的一个就是张果老，她明明已是个老太婆了，却还是打扮得花枝招展的，在妓院里混，一喝醉了，就会说些半疯半癫，别人听不懂的话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yin",
      "speaker_name": "杜吟",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "奇怪的是，偏偏还有很多人特地跑去看她，她的客人反而比别人多。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_du_yin",
      "text": "你们也是去看她的？也是她的客人？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yin",
      "speaker_name": "杜吟",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "是小霍拖我去的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我也是为了好奇，想去看看这个老妖怪，只可惜我们去得不巧，虽然见到她一面，但没有听到她那些妙论。",
      "tone": "遗憾",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_huo_ying",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "因为她的客人太多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我们本来还想多等一天的，可惜那地方今天已被人包下了。",
      "tone": "遗憾",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_huo_ying",
      "text": "被谁包下了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "被一个姓鱼的客人，听说是个豪客。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_huo_ying",
      "text": "这地方在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "就在春江城。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yin",
      "speaker_name": "杜吟",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "也就是我们遇见周至刚的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们走。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_huo_ying",
      "text": "当然是春江城的八仙船。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "八仙船在哪条街上？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yin",
      "speaker_name": "杜吟",
      "listener": "char_huo_ying",
      "text": "在桃花巷里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们闯进去。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "就这样闯进去？若是找错了地方怎么办？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "找错了就算他们倒霉。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "算他们倒霉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我若找不到人，就拆了他们的房子。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "可是他们并没有错，他们并没有要你们到这里来。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "text": "张果老。你们的客人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "speaker_name": "张果老",
      "listener": "char_huo_ying",
      "text": "我认得你，你昨天来过。可惜你今天却来迟了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "text": "难道人都已走了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "speaker_name": "张果老",
      "listener": "char_huo_ying",
      "text": "还没有走。他们不会走的，你就算用棍子赶他们，他们也不会走的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ying",
      "speaker_name": "霍英",
      "listener": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "speaker_name": "张果老",
      "listener": "char_huo_ying",
      "text": "你为什么不自己进去看看？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你还说我错恨了他？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不管怎么样，他绝不是你想像中那样无情的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他的确不是，他根本不能算是人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "难道你已认定了这些人是死在他手里的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "难道不是？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "绝不是，他从来也没有杀死过一个无辜的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "那么这些人是谁杀的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我可以问得出来，我一定要问出来，幸好这里还有一个活着的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "text": "你刚才一直都在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "text": "刚才这里发生的事，你都亲眼看见了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "speaker_name": "张果老",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我虽然已老了，却还看得见，也还听得见，我还没有死。那小子却以为我已经吓死了，我装死一定装得很像。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "text": "那小子杀人的时候，你也看见了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "speaker_name": "张果老",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "text": "这些人全都是他杀的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "speaker_name": "张果老",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他杀人杀得真快……他有把好快好快的刀。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 547
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "text": "你知道他是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "speaker_name": "张果老",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我当然知道，他是个死人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "text": "死人怎么会杀人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "speaker_name": "张果老",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "现在他虽然还没有死，可是他是个死人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "text": "他明明还活着，为什么是个死人……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "speaker_name": "张果老",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "因为他要杀人，别人一定也要杀他，他一定也活不长的，所以在我眼里看来，他根本就已是个死人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 563
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "text": "不管他是死是活，你能不能告诉我，他姓什么？长得是什么样子？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_guo_lao",
      "speaker_name": "张果老",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他长得很好看，是个男人……我喜欢男人，尤其喜欢好看的男人，可是……为什么越好看的男人，心就越狠呢……为什么越好看的男人就越无情……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "人上人他们今天请的就是他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你跟他分手的时候，他就是要到这里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "所以他一定来过。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "现在他却已走了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他们活着的时候，绝不会放他走的，因为他们找他来，就是为了对付他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
